    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Classification comprising two families of hominoids, Hylobatidae, including the gibbons and other lesser apes, and Hominidae, including gorillas, chimpanzees, orangutans, and humans, known as the great apes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
